Dialogue: 1,1:51:55.78,1:52:02.28,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}So I prayed as I stroked my belly
Dialogue: 1,1:52:08.81,1:52:15.60,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}I wondered what you would look like
Dialogue: 1,1:52:22.06,1:52:29.60,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}I wondered what you would sound like
Dialogue: 1,1:52:30.87,1:52:37.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}Now I see myself in your big eyes
Dialogue: 1,1:52:37.44,1:52:44.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}Tears run down your cheeks
Dialogue: 1,1:52:50.13,1:52:56.88,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}Come on, dinner is ready
Dialogue: 1,1:53:02.73,1:53:09.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}Come on, let us take a walk
Dialogue: 1,1:53:10.58,1:53:17.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}You've cried enough and hug your knees
Dialogue: 1,1:53:17.10,1:53:23.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}I ask you what is wrong, and you tell me everything
Dialogue: 1,1:53:23.74,1:53:29.96,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}Don't worry, I'll stay with you
Dialogue: 1,1:53:29.96,1:53:36.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}I will be with you, whatever may come
Dialogue: 1,1:53:36.63,1:53:42.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}I love how you laugh
Dialogue: 1,1:53:42.87,1:53:49.13,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}You cheer me up when I need it
Dialogue: 1,1:53:55.01,1:54:01.37,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}Come on, let us sing
Dialogue: 1,1:54:07.08,1:54:13.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}Come on, let us purr
Dialogue: 1,1:54:19.53,1:54:26.71,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}Don't rush growing up
Dialogue: 1,1:54:27.76,1:54:39.55,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}You run through the snow, count the clouds, play in the rain and wind
Dialogue: 1,1:54:39.55,1:54:51.19,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}Let us play the flute in a bed of flowers, with four legs or with two
Dialogue: 1,1:54:51.19,1:54:53.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}A new dawn
Dialogue: 1,1:54:53.94,1:54:56.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}A new day
Dialogue: 1,1:54:56.83,1:55:02.55,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}They're there for you
Dialogue: 1,1:55:02.55,1:55:05.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}A new dawn
Dialogue: 1,1:55:05.20,1:55:08.13,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}A new light
Dialogue: 1,1:55:08.13,1:55:13.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}The world is there for you
Dialogue: 1,1:55:13.82,1:55:16.67,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}A new dawn
Dialogue: 1,1:55:16.67,1:55:19.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}A new rainbow
Dialogue: 1,1:55:19.40,1:55:25.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}The world is full of mysteries
Dialogue: 1,1:55:25.09,1:55:37.71,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}I will watch you from afar as you pick a path to walk
Dialogue: 1,1:55:44.20,1:55:49.85,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}Is there really nothing else
Dialogue: 1,1:55:51.01,1:55:59.12,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,500)}I can do for you?
Dialogue: 1,1:55:59.12,1:56:17.60,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}I will see you off with a smile when the time comes
Dialogue: 1,1:56:23.22,1:56:29.36,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,350)}Perhaps it will feel a bit sad
Dialogue: 1,1:56:35.23,1:56:42.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(250,350)}Please, live a good life
